response_parts.content:
{
  "response": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "translated": "Hello, everyone."
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "translated": "Welcome to Project Sekai After Talk: Beyond the Untangled Threads Edition."
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "translated": "I'm Izumi Rina, the voice of Hinomori Shizuku"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "translated": "from MORE MORE JUMP! It's a pleasure to be here."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "translated": "This After Talk is a broadcast where we look back at the event story"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "translated": "and enjoy the After Live together. This is the 'Beyond the Untangled Threads' edition."
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "translated": "The event just finished a moment ago. How did you all like the story?"
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "translated": "I have so much I want to talk about!"
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "translated": "Wasn't it amazing?"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "translated": "So many things happened, and I want to talk about them today."
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "translated": "I'm looking forward to it."
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "translated": "Please post your thoughts on the event using the hashtag #ProsekaAfterTalk."
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "translated": "The staff has set up the YouTube chat so I can see it right here,"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "translated": "and I'll be reading your comments as we go."
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "translated": "The management provided a device again, so I'll use it"
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "translated": "to look at the story and the illustrations of the members with you."
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "translated": "For today's After Live, I'll be operating the device myself"
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "translated": "to join a room and watch the live show with you all."
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "translated": "I'll create a room ID right before the After Live starts"
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "translated": "so we can all enter it at the same time."
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "translated": "You might need to switch devices or apps, so I'd appreciate it"
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "translated": "if you could get everything ready now."
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "translated": "Thank you for your cooperation."
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "translated": "Now, let's look back at the event."
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "translated": "We're reviewing the story for 'Beyond the Untangled Threads'."
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "translated": "I see comments like, \"The entertainment industry is so scary,\""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "translated": "and many other things."
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "translated": "I really felt that the way Shizuku faced her past"
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "translated": "was so cool when I first read the script."
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "translated": "The story really depicts the realistic behind-the-scenes side of things."
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "translated": "There were some quite painful scenes, but because Shizuku"
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "translated": "faced them head-on without running away, she was able"
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "translated": "to reach that kind of conclusion to the story."
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "translated": "I really want to tell Shizuku she did a great job,"
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "translated": "and say thank you to the members of MORE MORE JUMP!"
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "translated": "I'll talk more in-depth about it later."
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "translated": "I'd like to watch one episode with everyone here today."
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "translated": "Which episode would you like to see?"
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "translated": "Personally..."
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "translated": "I want to see the intense battle during the filming of I-Hazard."
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "translated": "What about you?"
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "translated": "Episode 7 or 8?"
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "translated": "What do you all think?"
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "translated": "Regarding the story of her past..."
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "translated": "We've seen fragments of her time in Cheerful＊Days before,"
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "translated": "but this time it really delved deep into what specifically happened."
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "translated": "It's hard to choose, but maybe 7 or 8?"
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "translated": "It looks like there are a lot of votes for 7."
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "translated": "Should we go with 7?"
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "translated": "Is 7 okay with everyone?"
    }
  ]
}

